  "text": "The experimental protocol was as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Briefly, 60 male Wistar rats were randomly assigned to an untrained (UT, n = 30) or trained (T, n = 30) group. The rats had access to water ad libitum, were fed Labofeed B, and were maintained in a 12 h light/12 h dark cycle during the entire period of the study.",
